{
  "text": "What remains to show is that BID can be embedded into the infinitary system BID \u221e . In a first step we show that every instance of MIN is cut-free provable in BID \u221e with length \u03c9 + m for some m \u2208 N (cf. Generalized Induction Theorem 28.10 in [CITATION_1] ). ",
